description:
-Look at the value of Tom Brady in Tampa and how New England is falling apart without him

-We said Let Russ Cook not have to run the whole damn restaurant

-The Cowboys need to admit their mistake and fire everyone

-Colin was impressed by Joe Burrow, not Baker Mayfield

-Where Colin was right, where Colin was wrong


Guest: Trent Dilfer, Super Bowl Champion
